race.comment: LIVALITTLE (5) placed in town at the latest effort and should find this assignment a touch easier. Gets the reliable Gollan/Maloney combination and should get a gun run in transit from gate two. Has upside and will be right there when the whips are cracking. HAZEY HILL (1) is one from one over this track and trip and is sure to give backers a sight up on speed. Top-three conveyance. The well-related RUGBY (7) (half to G3 winner and 3xG2 placed Mallory) will be ready to peak now third-up from the spell and looks a must for the multiples. PELE PRINCESS (9) makes some appeal third-up and may earn some minor money. PRIDE OF SAVABELLA (3) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be underestimated.
